	heroEyebrow={`A Father For`}
	heroSubhead={`The pressure is real — the inbox that never empties, the fear of layoffs, the burnout you can't shake, the quiet question of who you are when the work stops. Here's the truth underneath the job title: you have a Father in heaven who already delights in you, apart from anything you produce.`}
