	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a manager`, bodyHtml: `Most Bibles can read like a list of expectations — one more boss grading your effort. The Father's Heart Bible™ reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. So instead of one more voice telling you to perform, you meet the One who already delights in you.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen on the commute, on your lunch break, or when the work stress keeps you up at night. The Father's voice fits right into your workday.` },
